                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="13702718" author="guozhang" created="Tue, 9 Jul 2013 00:54:38 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Proposed code change:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;1. Add a Map&amp;lt;Topic, PartitionIndex&amp;gt; to DefaultEventHandller.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;2. At the start of handle(events: Seq[KeyedMessage&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;K,V&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;]) function, clear the map.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;3. In getPartition function, if key == null, check if there is already an entry in the map with the given topic:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;3.1. If not, choose one partition from the availablePartitions, and add that partition to the map, return this partition index.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;3.2. If yes, check if its leaderBrokerIdOpt is defined; if yes, return this partition index directly, otherwise throw an exception.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13719025" author="guozhang" created="Wed, 24 Jul 2013 23:40:58 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Passed unit tests&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
